headline: Why Intel (INTC) Stock Is Falling Today
summary: Shares of computer processor maker Intel (NASDAQ:INTC) fell 5.8% in the morning session after a Bank of America analyst downgraded the stock to "underperform" from "neutral," citing concerns that the shares had climbed "too far, too fast."
